            "text": "The riftweasel Burrows into the carcass of a Large or larger adjacent creature, then Hides. As long as it remains inside a carcass, it can sense the surrounding area via tremorsense, and gains greater cover. A riftweasel doesn't need to hold its breath while burrowed into a carcass.",
